The paper discusses the use of machine learning methods for automated invention of ATP strategies, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of hierarchical extension and fine-tuning also suggests the involvement of machine learning techniques such as deep learning, which is commonly associated with the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of clause weight functions, which is a topic related to software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the paper deals with theorem proving, which is a topic related to logic (cs.LO).
